            "body": "LGTM. tests live in `test/unit/vterm_spec.lua`, should some coverage be added there? perhaps in the \"pen\" section: https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/583308f5991c4c55d3f04e456254d95433033c72/test/unit/vterm_spec.lua#L3444\r\n\r\nYou can [run the test](https://neovim.io/doc/user/dev_test.html#dev-filter-test) like this:\r\n\r\n    make unittest TEST_FILE=test/unit/vterm_spec.lua\r\n\r\n",
